      "text": [
        ": قال أبو جعفر عليه السلام: تابع بين الوضوء كما قال الله عز وجل ابدأ بالوجه … ابدأ بما بدأ الله عز وجل به"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "3. [3/85] al-Kafi: Ali from his father AND Muhammad b. Ismail from al-Fadhl b. Shadhan all together from Hammad from Hariz from Zurara who said: Abu Ja’far said عليه السلام: follow in the Wudhu the way Allāh Mighty and Majestic said – begin with the face… begin with what Allāh Mighty and Majestic began with."
        ]
      }
